{"tid":1242643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"621我哋唔要反送中喇","createTime":"2019-06-19T06:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:45:31.000Z","uid":174549,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b99ac42b7f3a33d19577255c4a256476dfb372d7","tid":1242643,"uid":174549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:33:48.000Z","msg":"其實又要衝又要光環，就一定要出師有名，<br />\n唔係講緊反送中呢個大議題，<br />\n因為<strong>好多溫和派/首遊都覺得「暫緩」咗就收貨</strong>，<br />\n佢哋已經下咗啖氣，<br />\n你再衝，佢已經覺得你做多咗。<br />\n<br />\n反而龍匯道警察向和平集會區發大量催淚彈呢單嘢，盧偉聰從來冇正面回應，<br />\n而警監會係廢既呢個事實都係全香港有共識，<br />\n勇武要衝，會唔會以此為名，要求立法會優先處理？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">將69至612以來濫用警權既議題擺上枱，</span><br />\n咁做亦可以向政府/立法會施壓，<br />\n保障被拘捕既手足。<br />\n<br />\n我哋要keep住搵一個群情最激烈既topic嚟煲！<br />\n唔好俾場運動急降溫！"},{"pid":"74aa2be19748aadf75dfc5cb7264d42ca432ffe5","tid":1242643,"uid":174549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02ea23e87338aeb9c1faf03b13437234a5253c23","tid":1242643,"uid":174549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03967f6903600de2ffdaa74141475800e787b601","tid":1242643,"uid":174549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b038db9aa987a5ebe68444ee2dba3cccf120208","tid":1242643,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:38:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02493d8d5a7518eff05187275910ce6c6177a84c","tid":1242643,"uid":174549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f330fa2e8641f8ad9ff96e255ef5fe355e48da13","tid":1242643,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"唔解決暴動論同埋警察濫權<br />\n好快就忘記，等同縱容政府再降底線<br />\n下次唔駛再玩"},{"pid":"ccce0c4570a3c2fced11019eb413974c7589fa89","tid":1242643,"uid":174549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f330fa2e8641f8ad9ff96e255ef5fe355e48